5
00:00:18.670 --> 00:00:19.420
One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece

6
00:01:47.670 --> 00:01:55.510
The Ruins of Oden Castle

7
00:01:59.680 --> 00:02:01.570
Big Bro!

8
00:02:03.260 --> 00:02:05.680
Boss Holdem!

9
00:02:05.680 --> 00:02:09.100
– Boss Holdem!
– Boss Holdem!

10
00:02:30.370 --> 00:02:31.720
Tama!

11
00:02:35.340 --> 00:02:37.720
Big Bro!

12
00:02:38.260 --> 00:02:40.730
Hold on tight!

13
00:02:40.730 --> 00:02:41.890
I will!

14
00:02:46.930 --> 00:02:49.350
Alright! Let's run!

15
00:02:58.730 --> 00:03:00.530
Boss Holdem!

16
00:03:00.530 --> 00:03:02.150
Boss Holdem!

17
00:03:05.330 --> 00:03:09.610
No way...! He beat
a headliner with one blow?!

18
00:03:10.290 --> 00:03:11.960
Who is he?!

19
00:03:17.930 --> 00:03:20.800
Luffy, you moron! Now you've done it...

20
00:03:20.800 --> 00:03:22.590
Luffytaro!

21
00:03:22.590 --> 00:03:24.250
Otama!

22
00:03:24.250 --> 00:03:28.270
Don't worry! Leave the kid to Luffytaro!

23
00:03:28.270 --> 00:03:31.560
Keep going! We need to reach
the town's entrance!

24
00:03:37.110 --> 00:03:42.480
Take back the treasure ship!
We can't lose our food!

25
00:03:48.990 --> 00:03:51.160
Hold on tight!

26
00:03:51.160 --> 00:03:54.170
Okay, Big Bro! I won't let go no matter what!

27
00:03:59.600 --> 00:04:01.760
B-Big Bro...

28
00:04:01.760 --> 00:04:03.680
Slice him up!

29
00:04:33.460 --> 00:04:36.130
Outta the way!

30
00:04:45.890 --> 00:04:50.460
I've gotta catch up to Zoro before
they eat all the good stuff!

31
00:04:54.020 --> 00:04:56.650
That's perfect! Let's hitch
a ride! I'm gonna jump!

32
00:04:56.650 --> 00:04:57.100
Huh?

33
00:05:00.270 --> 00:05:01.730
Who's there?!

34
00:05:01.730 --> 00:05:05.220
Who's holding me in his arms?!

35
00:05:05.220 --> 00:05:07.410
Giddyup, horse!

36
00:05:07.410 --> 00:05:08.740
Wait, what're you doing?!

37
00:05:08.740 --> 00:05:11.490
– What?! She's a human?!
– What?! She's a human?!

38
00:05:13.450 --> 00:05:14.750
No, she's a horse!

39
00:05:14.750 --> 00:05:17.080
How dare you get on Madam Speed like that?!

40
00:05:17.080 --> 00:05:18.420
Yank them down!

41
00:05:18.420 --> 00:05:22.010
Get off of me, you jackasses!

42
00:05:24.270 --> 00:05:26.580
Hey, Tama, make a dumpling!

43
00:05:26.580 --> 00:05:27.260
What?!

44
00:05:27.260 --> 00:05:29.350
Just do it!

45
00:05:29.350 --> 00:05:31.890
Millet Dumpling!

46
00:05:31.890 --> 00:05:33.220
Now, tame the horse!

47
00:05:33.220 --> 00:05:37.080
What? That's impossible!
It doesn't work on humans!

48
00:05:37.080 --> 00:05:39.400
You don't know until you try!

49
00:05:42.360 --> 00:05:44.430
That looks delicious!

50
00:05:55.540 --> 00:06:00.200
Where would you like to go, Master?!

51
00:06:00.200 --> 00:06:01.870
You did it!

52
00:06:01.870 --> 00:06:03.710
It worked!

53
00:06:04.420 --> 00:06:06.200
But... why?

54
00:06:06.200 --> 00:06:08.430
She's half-horse, isn't she?

55
00:06:10.840 --> 00:06:13.490
Madam Speed...

56
00:06:13.490 --> 00:06:15.350
After her!

57
00:06:18.870 --> 00:06:19.900
She's too fast!

58
00:06:19.900 --> 00:06:23.420
Alright, Horsella! Follow that treasure ship!

59
00:06:23.420 --> 00:06:25.690
I'm not your servant!

60
00:06:25.690 --> 00:06:29.950
My name is Speed! Don't call me Horsella
like we're friends or something!

61
00:06:29.950 --> 00:06:34.160
I want you to do as Big Bro says, Horsella.

62
00:06:36.410 --> 00:06:40.370
Of course, Master!

63
00:06:40.370 --> 00:06:44.820
I can't believe a headliner
like Speed is obeying them!

64
00:06:44.820 --> 00:06:47.260
Do they have some kind of dirt on her?

65
00:06:52.180 --> 00:06:54.180
Big Bro...

66
00:06:55.250 --> 00:06:58.230
Red Hawk!

67
00:06:59.440 --> 00:07:01.520
Fire Fist!

68
00:07:08.890 --> 00:07:12.280
Big Bro... Back there...

69
00:07:14.710 --> 00:07:16.990
you were just like Ace.

70
00:07:22.250 --> 00:07:24.380
Hm? What?

71
00:07:24.380 --> 00:07:25.990
Did you say something?

72
00:07:30.800 --> 00:07:31.920
No!

73
00:07:32.800 --> 00:07:34.600
Never mind.

74
00:07:45.580 --> 00:07:47.400
Your life is mine.

75
00:07:47.400 --> 00:07:49.150
What'd you say?!

76
00:07:51.320 --> 00:07:52.880
Take him out!

77
00:07:52.880 --> 00:07:53.740
– Yeah!
– Yeah!

78
00:07:53.740 --> 00:07:55.240
Room!

79
00:07:57.780 --> 00:08:00.000
That ability...

80
00:08:00.650 --> 00:08:02.210
Those tattoos...

81
00:08:03.000 --> 00:08:03.960
Is he...?!

82
00:08:09.490 --> 00:08:10.950
He could be!

83
00:08:11.340 --> 00:08:14.010
They did have an alliance!

84
00:08:18.850 --> 00:08:23.350
Roronoa is with that group
but at least he knows the plan.

85
00:08:24.180 --> 00:08:29.300
He surely wouldn't do anything stupid
like taking down Holdem.

86
00:08:30.730 --> 00:08:33.360
Boss Holdem!

87
00:08:33.360 --> 00:08:37.570
This is bad! We've gotta
report this to Master Jack!

88
00:08:37.570 --> 00:08:39.450
If they were to do something to him...

89
00:08:39.450 --> 00:08:42.010
that would be it...

90
00:08:42.600 --> 00:08:43.540
for our plan...

91
00:08:47.130 --> 00:08:49.810
Get lost, Hawkins!

92
00:08:52.800 --> 00:08:53.800
Shambles!

93
00:09:12.470 --> 00:09:14.360
Help me!

94
00:09:14.360 --> 00:09:17.740
Wait?! How am I alive?!

95
00:09:17.740 --> 00:09:21.990
What the hell?! His lower
body's moving by itself!

96
00:09:24.960 --> 00:09:28.290
Just... what kind of ability was that?

97
00:09:29.130 --> 00:09:30.970
Straw Sword!

98
00:09:32.210 --> 00:09:33.720
Take off your mask...

99
00:09:34.300 --> 00:09:36.610
Trafalgar Law!

100
00:09:57.570 --> 00:10:02.450
I knew it wasn't gonna be
that easy, Basil Hawkins!

101
00:10:03.180 --> 00:10:03.910
But...

102
00:10:06.200 --> 00:10:09.920
Blah, blah, blah! Time to shut you up!

103
00:10:09.920 --> 00:10:11.880
Get him!

104
00:10:11.880 --> 00:10:12.590
Wait!

105
00:10:19.600 --> 00:10:21.090
Amputate!

106
00:10:27.390 --> 00:10:28.350
Takt!

107
00:10:37.740 --> 00:10:38.860
Shambles!

108
00:10:59.580 --> 00:11:01.800
You cut up all my proxies.

109
00:11:01.800 --> 00:11:04.470
You certainly adapt quickly.

110
00:11:04.470 --> 00:11:06.010
I was just bluffing.

111
00:11:06.780 --> 00:11:10.270
Murder isn't my style. I am a doctor, after all.

112
00:11:11.710 --> 00:11:16.320
Welcome to Wano. It's been some time
since that fateful day at Sabaody.

113
00:11:16.320 --> 00:11:21.280
Since your allies are here too,
I'm assuming you're not here as a tourist.

114
00:11:22.620 --> 00:11:24.700
You thought I didn't know?

115
00:11:24.700 --> 00:11:27.660
I've already crossed paths
with Straw Hat's group.

116
00:11:29.310 --> 00:11:33.120
If you were looking to silence me,
I'm afraid it's too late.

117
00:11:38.890 --> 00:11:43.220
The thieves fled after defeating Boss Holdem!

118
00:11:43.220 --> 00:11:45.300
We've already informed Master Jack!

119
00:11:45.300 --> 00:11:49.770
They beat Holdem and now
Jack has been notified?

120
00:11:50.060 --> 00:11:55.080
As you just heard, your efforts were in vain.

121
00:11:56.130 --> 00:12:02.400
And of course, this means Captain Kaido
will become aware of these goings on.

122
00:12:04.650 --> 00:12:09.630
Those morons! This is
the worst-case scenario!

123
00:12:13.960 --> 00:12:18.020
Hey, you guys! Get out the way!

124
00:12:18.020 --> 00:12:19.460
Roronoa?!

125
00:12:19.460 --> 00:12:23.350
Excuse us! We need to pass! We're in a hurry!

126
00:12:33.180 --> 00:12:36.440
Get them! They stole our food!

127
00:12:43.110 --> 00:12:45.090
Roronoa!

128
00:12:45.090 --> 00:12:46.780
Oh, Traffy.

129
00:12:48.030 --> 00:12:49.200
You idiot!

130
00:13:05.590 --> 00:13:07.260
Is there a problem, Traffy?

131
00:13:07.260 --> 00:13:09.100
Screw you!

132
00:13:09.100 --> 00:13:11.470
What?! Who is that?!

133
00:13:13.020 --> 00:13:17.350
Not only did you become a fugitive,
you drew Jack's attention!

134
00:13:17.350 --> 00:13:21.350
You promised that you were
gonna stay out of trouble!

135
00:13:22.220 --> 00:13:23.570
My bad.

136
00:13:23.570 --> 00:13:25.360
Also...

137
00:13:25.360 --> 00:13:27.450
why are you even in Kuri?!

138
00:13:27.450 --> 00:13:31.410
You were supposed to pose as
a ronin in the Flower Capital!

139
00:13:32.310 --> 00:13:33.540
They know each other?

140
00:13:33.540 --> 00:13:35.520
Is everything okay?

141
00:13:35.520 --> 00:13:36.790
No, it's not!

142
00:13:36.790 --> 00:13:38.260
I'm sorry!

143
00:13:38.630 --> 00:13:41.240
I had no choice!

144
00:13:41.240 --> 00:13:43.550
I ran into Luffy.

145
00:13:45.170 --> 00:13:48.890
Straw Hat! It's always him!

146
00:13:58.690 --> 00:14:01.060
Zorojuro! We're leaving town!

147
00:14:01.910 --> 00:14:03.550
Alright...

148
00:14:03.550 --> 00:14:05.780
Let's unload at Okobore Town!

149
00:14:07.780 --> 00:14:11.000
Mom! I'm hungry!

150
00:14:11.000 --> 00:14:12.740
You have to endure it.

151
00:14:19.020 --> 00:14:20.330
What is it?

152
00:14:30.470 --> 00:14:32.220
Th-That's...

153
00:14:32.220 --> 00:14:35.320
a treasure ship!

154
00:14:35.640 --> 00:14:38.520
There are so many fish!

155
00:14:38.520 --> 00:14:41.120
Food! There's food!

156
00:14:56.330 --> 00:14:58.040
A treasure ship is here!

157
00:14:58.040 --> 00:15:01.370
We're saved!

158
00:15:03.790 --> 00:15:05.590
Amazing!

159
00:15:05.590 --> 00:15:07.880
Hurry, everyone!

160
00:15:39.650 --> 00:15:41.540
It's food!

161
00:15:41.540 --> 00:15:43.400
Can we have it?!

162
00:15:43.400 --> 00:15:44.950
Thank goodness!

163
00:15:44.950 --> 00:15:46.340
We can survive!

164
00:15:47.010 --> 00:15:49.300
It's delicious!

165
00:15:49.930 --> 00:15:53.260
There's so much food!

166
00:15:53.910 --> 00:15:57.220
We won't starve! This is so great!

167
00:15:58.050 --> 00:16:00.060
What a relief...

168
00:16:07.400 --> 00:16:10.030
Whoa-whoa-whoa, wait!

169
00:16:10.030 --> 00:16:12.740
Those aren't leftovers yet!

170
00:16:12.740 --> 00:16:15.620
Stay away from the treasure ship!

171
00:16:16.620 --> 00:16:18.990
You trash!

172
00:16:18.990 --> 00:16:23.870
You shouldn't even be touching that food!

173
00:16:23.870 --> 00:16:26.750
You idiots forgot your place!

174
00:16:27.540 --> 00:16:29.550
We won't let you pass!

175
00:16:29.550 --> 00:16:31.840
So you're siding with the trash!

176
00:16:31.840 --> 00:16:35.220
This is coming out of your hides, you fools!

177
00:16:39.260 --> 00:16:41.270
Hey!

178
00:16:42.180 --> 00:16:44.900
Sorry to keep you waiting!

179
00:16:55.320 --> 00:16:57.660
It's water!

180
00:17:00.040 --> 00:17:03.910
It won't poison you! Help yourselves!

181
00:17:15.670 --> 00:17:19.260
It's been years since we've had
this much drinking water!

182
00:17:19.260 --> 00:17:21.930
Thank goodness! Thank goodness!

183
00:17:23.850 --> 00:17:27.980
I'm Luffytaro, in case anyone comes and asks!

184
00:17:37.020 --> 00:17:39.820
Thank you, Luffytaro!

185
00:17:39.820 --> 00:17:42.200
Big Bro!

186
00:17:43.220 --> 00:17:44.160
Tama!

187
00:17:45.370 --> 00:17:46.660
Oh?

188
00:17:46.660 --> 00:17:48.080
Traffy!

189
00:17:48.080 --> 00:17:50.290
It's good to see you!

190
00:17:50.290 --> 00:17:52.050
Straw Hat...

191
00:17:52.050 --> 00:17:55.760
in Wano, this is considered an insurrection.

192
00:17:55.760 --> 00:17:58.990
An insurrection? This is nothing like that!

193
00:18:00.910 --> 00:18:01.600
Here!

194
00:18:07.220 --> 00:18:08.900
It's an apple!

195
00:18:09.650 --> 00:18:10.970
Tama...

196
00:18:14.180 --> 00:18:18.780
I'm paying you back for feeding me.

197
00:18:18.780 --> 00:18:21.150
This is just the start!

198
00:18:30.630 --> 00:18:32.710
Look at all this meat!

199
00:18:34.530 --> 00:18:36.630
Hey! Guys!

200
00:18:36.630 --> 00:18:38.630
Save some meat for me!

201
00:18:38.630 --> 00:18:41.730
Meat! Meat, meat!

202
00:18:41.730 --> 00:18:43.560
Meat, meat, meat, meat!

203
00:18:43.560 --> 00:18:45.170
Meat!

204
00:18:56.480 --> 00:18:58.280
Boss Holdem!

205
00:18:58.280 --> 00:19:00.450
The fire is spreading!

206
00:19:00.450 --> 00:19:02.680
Where are the firefighters?!

207
00:19:04.740 --> 00:19:07.670
Boss Holdem! Stay with us!

208
00:19:07.670 --> 00:19:10.120
Please wake up!

209
00:19:17.180 --> 00:19:20.180
Only the lion woke up! That's scary!

210
00:19:23.600 --> 00:19:25.350
That's right...

211
00:19:25.350 --> 00:19:28.730
It's Monkey D. Luffy, Roronoa Zoro,

212
00:19:28.730 --> 00:19:30.940
and Trafalgar Law.

213
00:19:31.600 --> 00:19:33.650
I don't want to sell myself short...

214
00:19:34.510 --> 00:19:39.610
but when the foe is as troublesome as
these three, it's too much even for me.

215
00:19:57.960 --> 00:20:00.950
It's so delicious!

216
00:20:01.690 --> 00:20:03.640
Good for you, Tama!

217
00:20:04.330 --> 00:20:05.470
Y-Yes!

218
00:20:05.470 --> 00:20:09.370
I don't know if I could ever top
a wonderful birthday like this!

219
00:20:09.370 --> 00:20:10.680
Tama!

220
00:20:10.680 --> 00:20:13.100
Don't set the bar too low!

221
00:20:13.100 --> 00:20:15.480
I'm gonna make this normal for you!

222
00:20:17.440 --> 00:20:20.440
Before we leave this country,

223
00:20:20.440 --> 00:20:24.280
I'll make it a place where you can
eat as much as you want!

224
00:20:47.710 --> 00:20:51.100
When we come back to this country...

225
00:20:51.100 --> 00:20:55.310
we'll make it a place where you can
eat as much as you want!

226
00:21:15.580 --> 00:21:17.000
Hm? You don't want that?

227
00:21:18.050 --> 00:21:19.000
What?!

228
00:21:19.080 --> 00:21:20.960
Wh-Wh-What?!

229
00:21:20.960 --> 00:21:23.130
O-Of course...

230
00:21:23.130 --> 00:21:26.120
Of course, and it makes me happy!

231
00:21:28.690 --> 00:21:30.760
It just surprised me a bit...!

232
00:21:34.490 --> 00:21:35.460
I see!

233
00:21:39.360 --> 00:21:42.900
Man! You've really gone and done it!

234
00:21:42.900 --> 00:21:46.990
Now, they'll really come after us!
Stay on your guard!

235
00:21:46.990 --> 00:21:48.660
Like you can talk!

236
00:21:49.160 --> 00:21:52.740
We shouldn't stick around here. Time to go!

237
00:21:53.980 --> 00:21:55.190
Follow me!

238
00:21:56.730 --> 00:22:00.920
We'll go to the ruins of Oden Castle
at the top of that mountain!

239
00:22:03.880 --> 00:22:06.050
Okay, I'm heading off too!

240
00:22:08.600 --> 00:22:10.650
Thank you!

241
00:22:10.650 --> 00:22:13.930
Alright, take good care of her, Horsella!

242
00:22:13.930 --> 00:22:18.820
I am Speed, a headliner of the Beast Pirates!

243
00:22:18.820 --> 00:22:21.440
I don't take orders from you, fool!

244
00:22:22.730 --> 00:22:25.820
Servants naturally protect their masters!

245
00:22:25.820 --> 00:22:29.860
Why is a headliner obeying that kid?

246
00:22:31.110 --> 00:22:32.200
Big Bro...

247
00:22:32.200 --> 00:22:34.100
Hm? What is it?

248
00:22:35.220 --> 00:22:38.210
I'll never forget...

249
00:22:43.130 --> 00:22:50.340
I'll never ever forget the taste of the oshiruko
soup and the apple that I had today!

250
00:22:50.340 --> 00:22:51.590
Great!

251
00:22:51.590 --> 00:22:56.970
When I return to Amigasa Village,
I'm gonna give this apple to my master!

252
00:22:56.970 --> 00:23:01.270
Say hi to Grandpa Nose for me!
I promise I'll bring back the dog!

253
00:23:01.270 --> 00:23:02.740
I will!

254
00:23:02.740 --> 00:23:03.860
Komachiyo!

255
00:23:03.860 --> 00:23:07.010
I want you to help Big Bro!

256
00:23:08.360 --> 00:23:09.820
Oh, yeah!

257
00:23:09.820 --> 00:23:15.180
Let me borrow this sword for a little longer!
Without it, I can't call myself a samurai!

258
00:23:15.180 --> 00:23:18.500
You're not even using it!

259
00:23:18.500 --> 00:23:22.080
Seriously, just let me take a look at it!

260
00:23:22.460 --> 00:23:25.460
I'll let my master know!

261
00:23:25.460 --> 00:23:27.330
Yeah, thanks!

262
00:23:27.330 --> 00:23:30.010
We must get going, Master!

263
00:23:30.010 --> 00:23:32.250
Oh, thank you!

264
00:23:32.250 --> 00:23:34.550
Have a safe journey!

265
00:23:34.550 --> 00:23:36.010
Okay! Well then...!

266
00:23:38.020 --> 00:23:40.940
See you around!

267
00:23:44.980 --> 00:23:47.070
See ya!

268
00:23:47.070 --> 00:23:49.810
Tama!

269
00:23:58.980 --> 00:24:00.120
All right...

270
00:24:00.120 --> 00:24:01.410
Luffy!

271
00:24:03.470 --> 00:24:04.750
Time to get going!

272
00:24:05.250 --> 00:24:06.920
Mr. Luffytaro!

273
00:24:09.010 --> 00:24:11.010
– Mr. Luffytaro!
– Mr. Luffytaro!

274
00:24:11.010 --> 00:24:13.890
I've never seen this much food before!

275
00:24:13.890 --> 00:24:16.000
My grandfather is better!

276
00:24:16.000 --> 00:24:18.010
I lived to see this dream come true!

277
00:24:18.010 --> 00:24:20.230
Our child is healthy again!

278
00:24:21.850 --> 00:24:25.310
I've never eaten this much before!

279
00:24:35.270 --> 00:24:36.610
That's good!

280
00:24:41.700 --> 00:24:43.920
All right, then!

281
00:24:43.920 --> 00:24:48.670
– Thank you for the treasure ship!
– Thank you for the treasure ship!

282
00:24:48.670 --> 00:24:50.640
– Thank you!
– Thank you!

283
00:24:50.640 --> 00:24:52.920
– Come visit again!
– Thank you!

284
00:24:53.710 --> 00:24:56.630
Pirates shouldn't be such do-gooders.

285
00:24:56.630 --> 00:24:57.640
It makes me sick!

286
00:24:59.510 --> 00:25:02.430
That was a nice thing we did!

287
00:25:04.760 --> 00:25:06.550
It's still theft.

288
00:25:10.360 --> 00:25:12.190
Guys!

289
00:25:12.190 --> 00:25:15.110
Take care of yourselves!

290
00:25:24.070 --> 00:25:27.810
You didn't become her servant
by eating that dumpling, huh?

291
00:25:29.710 --> 00:25:31.050
So...

292
00:25:31.050 --> 00:25:33.320
why are you coming with us?

293
00:25:34.110 --> 00:25:38.510
I-I'm sorry! I've always wanted
to visit Oden Castle!

294
00:25:38.510 --> 00:25:43.410
I will head home right after,
so I will not be a burden.

295
00:25:44.980 --> 00:25:46.500
Should I be worried?

296
00:25:47.310 --> 00:25:48.400
Nah!

297
00:25:48.400 --> 00:25:52.320
Kiku's a good, strong person,
so it's gonna be fine!

298
00:25:54.030 --> 00:25:55.400
Actually...

299
00:25:55.400 --> 00:25:57.970
she's hiding something!

300
00:25:58.980 --> 00:26:02.290
Hey, Traffy, why are we going to the castle?

301
00:26:02.290 --> 00:26:04.410
It's not a castle anymore...

302
00:26:05.070 --> 00:26:07.810
Only the deserted ruins remain.

303
00:26:07.810 --> 00:26:10.990
Why does he wanna go to Oden Castle?

304
00:26:11.540 --> 00:26:14.340
Luffytaro and his allies are good people...

305
00:26:14.340 --> 00:26:16.610
but I can't drop my guard yet.

306
00:26:18.590 --> 00:26:21.030
Since we last saw you...

307
00:26:21.030 --> 00:26:25.050
we made a plan and set about following it...

308
00:26:25.050 --> 00:26:28.020
You'll see once you get there.

309
00:26:28.020 --> 00:26:29.190
First...

310
00:26:29.190 --> 00:26:32.430
you're going to meet the ghosts of Wano.

311
00:26:34.110 --> 00:26:35.230
Ghosts?

312
00:26:36.380 --> 00:26:38.060
Get ready for a shock...

313
00:26:39.730 --> 00:26:43.280
Yeah... I was stunned, too.

314
00:26:47.650 --> 00:26:49.790
There, you'll learn...

315
00:26:52.540 --> 00:27:03.350
Retainer Kanjuro
Grave of...

316
00:26:54.050 --> 00:27:03.350
Retainer Raizo

317
00:26:55.670 --> 00:27:03.350
Retainer Kin'emon

318
00:26:57.050 --> 00:27:03.350
Kozuki Momonosuke

319
00:26:58.450 --> 00:27:01.680
an unbelievable truth!

320
00:26:58.760 --> 00:27:03.350
Kozuki Oden

321
00:27:05.710 --> 00:27:06.890
Anyway...

322
00:27:06.890 --> 00:27:11.730
we can continue this conversation once we
reach the ruins of Oden Castle at the summit.

323
00:27:13.400 --> 00:27:14.610
You're no fun!

324
00:27:24.780 --> 00:27:26.370
There's a threat.

325
00:27:26.370 --> 00:27:27.700
Yeah.

326
00:27:28.290 --> 00:27:30.250
Maybe it's one of Orochi's assassins.

327
00:27:30.250 --> 00:27:32.000
Luffy, you go on ahead.

328
00:27:32.910 --> 00:27:36.210
I'll catch up to you after I take care of this.

329
00:27:36.210 --> 00:27:37.170
Thanks.

330
00:27:42.720 --> 00:27:45.610
I can feel your bloodlust.

331
00:28:03.410 --> 00:28:05.240
There's no castle here!

332
00:28:05.240 --> 00:28:06.640
I did say "ruins."

333
00:28:05.280 --> 00:28:09.580
Ruins of Oden Castle
Kuri, Wano

334
00:28:06.640 --> 00:28:07.710
Oh, yeah.

335
00:28:07.710 --> 00:28:09.590
It's this way. Follow me.

336
00:28:16.620 --> 00:28:18.970
What? Hey, Kiku!

337
00:28:19.670 --> 00:28:21.470
What's wrong with her?

338
00:28:21.470 --> 00:28:25.180
Oh! Come to think of it,
Zoro hasn't returned yet, either.

339
00:28:31.560 --> 00:28:34.650
This place is creepy.

340
00:28:34.650 --> 00:28:37.400
It's been abandoned for twenty years.

341
00:28:41.930 --> 00:28:43.170
What are those?

342
00:28:47.780 --> 00:28:50.210
"Kozuki Oden..."?

343
00:28:52.540 --> 00:28:55.250
Look at the other graves, too.

344
00:28:57.400 --> 00:28:59.150
"Kozuki..."

345
00:28:59.750 --> 00:29:00.260
Mo-

346
00:29:00.260 --> 00:29:00.760
mo-

347
00:29:00.760 --> 00:29:01.260
no-

348
00:29:01.260 --> 00:29:01.710
suke

349
00:29:02.820 --> 00:29:04.720
Momonosuke is...

350
00:29:05.720 --> 00:29:09.050
You know the kid that grave belongs to.

351
00:29:09.050 --> 00:29:11.810
What?! What are you talking about, Traffy?!

352
00:29:11.810 --> 00:29:14.770
It's not just him.

353
00:29:18.360 --> 00:29:19.950
"Raizo"?!

354
00:29:21.820 --> 00:29:23.550
"Kanjuro"?!

355
00:29:25.150 --> 00:29:26.920
"Kin'emon"?!

356
00:29:30.120 --> 00:29:32.790
Why are their graves here?!

357
00:29:41.270 --> 00:29:44.320
Wait a minute, when we were
making our way to Wano...

358
00:29:44.320 --> 00:29:47.300
I couldn't get in touch with Kin'emon...

359
00:29:51.100 --> 00:29:53.560
Kin'emon

360
00:29:54.910 --> 00:29:57.120
D-Don't tell me...

361
00:30:03.320 --> 00:30:05.410
he's dead!

362
00:30:17.330 --> 00:30:19.350
Okay, time to head back.

363
00:30:22.600 --> 00:30:25.720
Where did they go?

364
00:30:30.710 --> 00:30:32.350
It's a dock.

365
00:30:47.530 --> 00:30:49.060
No way...

366
00:30:51.990 --> 00:30:53.660
They can't be dead!

367
00:30:53.660 --> 00:30:56.280
I thought Kin'emon was waiting here...

368
00:30:53.660 --> 00:30:55.490
Grave of Kin'emon

369
00:30:56.310 --> 00:30:58.870
He's been gone for quite a while.

370
00:30:58.870 --> 00:30:59.870
Gone?!

371
00:30:59.870 --> 00:31:02.330
He might emerge at night.

372
00:31:02.330 --> 00:31:04.990
He showed up repeated last night.

373
00:31:07.720 --> 00:31:10.510
That sounds like he's a ghost or something!

374
00:31:10.510 --> 00:31:14.930
What's up with these graves?!
Spit it out, Traffy!

375
00:31:14.930 --> 00:31:17.140
Is there something you don't wanna say?!

376
00:31:18.070 --> 00:31:20.810
I'm not the one who should
be telling you about it.

377
00:31:53.400 --> 00:31:55.220
Sir Luffy!

378
00:31:56.650 --> 00:31:57.140
What?

379
00:31:59.060 --> 00:32:00.060
Kin!

380
00:32:00.060 --> 00:32:02.730
I'm glad that you're alive!

381
00:32:02.730 --> 00:32:06.210
I'm sorry that I couldn't come to get you...

382
00:32:06.210 --> 00:32:08.570
It's so great that you arrived safely.

383
00:32:08.570 --> 00:32:12.000
I'm afraid I have a bad case of the runs.

384
00:32:12.000 --> 00:32:16.460
I thought I'd be confined to
the outhouse again tonight.

385
00:32:16.980 --> 00:32:20.370
But I'm starting to feel a little better.

386
00:32:17.080 --> 00:32:23.240
"Foxfire" Kin'emon
Retainer of the Kozuki Clan

387
00:32:20.370 --> 00:32:23.250
Well, at any rate, it was pretty bad.

388
00:32:23.250 --> 00:32:25.450
He's alive, Traffy!

389
00:32:25.450 --> 00:32:27.340
When did I say he wasn't?

390
00:32:27.340 --> 00:32:30.110
I meant he might emerge
from the bathroom tonight.

391
00:32:30.110 --> 00:32:31.920
That was misleading!

392
00:32:33.820 --> 00:32:35.390
Sir Kin!

393
00:32:35.510 --> 00:32:36.480
Kiku!

394
00:32:37.680 --> 00:32:40.770
You're back!

395
00:32:41.470 --> 00:32:42.940
I really missed you!

396
00:32:42.940 --> 00:32:44.810
I was so uneasy!

397
00:32:44.810 --> 00:32:46.270
Oh, really...

398
00:32:46.270 --> 00:32:51.940
Honestly! If you were back,
why didn't you come tell me?!

399
00:32:51.940 --> 00:32:55.280
I was worried about you. How cold of you!

400
00:32:55.280 --> 00:32:56.220
I-I'm sorry!

401
00:32:56.220 --> 00:32:57.990
Lord Momonosuke is okay, too?

402
00:32:57.990 --> 00:32:58.980
Yes.

403
00:32:58.980 --> 00:33:01.450
Momo's alive, too, huh?

404
00:33:01.450 --> 00:33:04.470
Wait, Kiku and Kin know each other?

405
00:33:04.470 --> 00:33:06.670
Seems like they're very close.

406
00:33:06.670 --> 00:33:07.170
What?

407
00:33:07.170 --> 00:33:11.710
Kiku, why are you with Sir Luffy?

408
00:33:11.710 --> 00:33:15.010
What?! Are these the ones who...?!

409
00:33:16.840 --> 00:33:20.030
I don't know who to tell what first...!

410
00:33:23.220 --> 00:33:24.980
But you are correct, Kiku!

411
00:33:24.980 --> 00:33:28.730
They are strong allies that are going
to help us take down Orochi!

412
00:33:28.730 --> 00:33:31.810
Sir Luffy and Sir Law!

413
00:33:31.810 --> 00:33:33.360
Wow!

414
00:33:33.360 --> 00:33:35.820
Hey, Luffy!

415
00:33:36.820 --> 00:33:38.700
You arrived safely!

416
00:33:39.890 --> 00:33:40.990
Lord Momonosuke?!

417
00:33:40.990 --> 00:33:45.070
Luffy, I was just practicing
my swordsmanship!

418
00:33:45.070 --> 00:33:46.020
Good!

419
00:33:46.020 --> 00:33:46.880
Watch this!

420
00:33:49.080 --> 00:33:52.210
Lord Momonosuke, I'm glad that you're okay!

421
00:33:52.210 --> 00:33:54.720
Indeed, Kiku. It'd been a while.

422
00:33:54.720 --> 00:33:58.430
Is Dog Pops here in Wano, too, Momo?

423
00:33:58.430 --> 00:33:59.640
What? Momo?!

424
00:33:59.640 --> 00:34:03.590
It's rude to address
Lord Momonosuke so casually!

425
00:34:04.020 --> 00:34:06.020
Oh, it's fine, Kiku.

426
00:34:06.020 --> 00:34:07.440
What? Okay.

427
00:34:07.440 --> 00:34:10.770
Of course, Inuarashi is here, too.

428
00:34:10.770 --> 00:34:12.730
So he is!

429
00:34:13.930 --> 00:34:16.010
So that just leaves the others now.

430
00:34:16.610 --> 00:34:20.310
Are we there yet?
We've been walking for ages.

431
00:34:20.310 --> 00:34:25.690
He said to look for the castle ruins,
so it has to be on this mountain.

432
00:34:25.690 --> 00:34:28.210
I'm glad that we finally got in touch with him!

433
00:34:30.290 --> 00:34:32.030
Hey!

434
00:34:33.920 --> 00:34:36.840
Luffy, there you are!

435
00:34:36.840 --> 00:34:38.340
– Luffy!
– Luffy!

436
00:34:38.340 --> 00:34:40.760
Guys! Over here!

437
00:34:40.760 --> 00:34:42.220
Luffy!

438
00:34:42.220 --> 00:34:44.470
I'm glad that you're okay!

439
00:34:46.310 --> 00:34:48.650
Garchu!

440
00:34:48.650 --> 00:34:52.360
Luffy! You're dressed like
a samurai! That's so cool!

441
00:34:52.360 --> 00:34:53.980
What took you guys so long?!

442
00:34:53.980 --> 00:34:57.570
We even searched the seabed for you!

443
00:34:57.570 --> 00:35:01.820
We found your vivre card,
so we knew you were alive, at least.

444
00:35:01.820 --> 00:35:03.410
Onami!

445
00:35:03.410 --> 00:35:04.780
Momo!

446
00:35:04.780 --> 00:35:07.400
Kin'emon, how are you doing?

447
00:35:07.400 --> 00:35:08.830
I'm getting by.

448
00:35:08.830 --> 00:35:11.770
Momonosuke, you look good.

449
00:35:12.330 --> 00:35:14.250
I thought so, you dirty brat!

450
00:35:14.250 --> 00:35:17.490
So you've returned to the crew, Sir Sanji.

451
00:35:17.490 --> 00:35:19.770
Yeah, sorry to make you worry.

452
00:35:19.770 --> 00:35:20.900
Kin!

453
00:35:23.180 --> 00:35:27.560
Are these some of Luffytaro's friends?

454
00:35:27.560 --> 00:35:30.140
What a lovely lady!

455
00:35:31.980 --> 00:35:33.270
Hey!

456
00:35:33.280 --> 00:35:35.450
That's enough! Get off of her!

457
00:35:35.450 --> 00:35:37.280
You're being insolent, Bonekichi!

458
00:35:37.280 --> 00:35:39.560
Leave him alone, Brook!

459
00:35:39.560 --> 00:35:40.900
Right, Momo?

460
00:35:40.900 --> 00:35:43.300
Onami...

461
00:35:41.870 --> 00:35:43.300
Momo!

462
00:35:43.700 --> 00:35:45.860
Momo!

463
00:35:45.860 --> 00:35:48.830
These are indeed Sir Luffy's friends.

464
00:35:48.830 --> 00:35:51.700
The people we will rely on!

465
00:35:56.870 --> 00:36:00.810
Lord Momonosuke, I'm glad
you're able to smile again.

466
00:36:02.630 --> 00:36:04.390
Captain!

467
00:36:04.390 --> 00:36:06.180
Oh, you guys.

468
00:36:06.180 --> 00:36:08.090
How's Bepo doing?

469
00:36:08.090 --> 00:36:11.560
He hasn't come out of the bush yet.
He's still got the runs.

470
00:36:12.780 --> 00:36:14.690
What's wrong with everyone?

471
00:36:16.490 --> 00:36:17.360
Straw Hat.

472
00:36:17.360 --> 00:36:18.090
Huh?

473
00:36:18.090 --> 00:36:20.020
Let's talk inside.

474
00:36:20.020 --> 00:36:21.080
Okay.

475
00:36:21.080 --> 00:36:24.330
We stole safe food from the farm.

476
00:36:24.330 --> 00:36:26.830
So you're the one who did it!

477
00:36:29.200 --> 00:36:32.620
This ruined castle will be our headquarters.

478
00:36:42.720 --> 00:36:44.850
What a messy room!

479
00:36:44.850 --> 00:36:46.760
I'm sorry, everyone...

480
00:36:54.060 --> 00:36:56.940
Sir Luffy! Everyone!

481
00:36:56.940 --> 00:36:59.860
Thank you for coming to Wano!

482
00:37:00.470 --> 00:37:03.110
As ever, I am extremely grateful!

483
00:37:03.110 --> 00:37:04.820
Don't mention it!

484
00:37:04.820 --> 00:37:06.070
Yeah!

485
00:37:07.380 --> 00:37:11.350
First things first, there is a secret
we haven't told you about...

486
00:37:11.350 --> 00:37:15.920
aside from Lord Momonosuke's true identity.

487
00:37:17.130 --> 00:37:19.380
You guys have so many secrets!

488
00:37:19.380 --> 00:37:22.880
Just tell us everything already!
You can trust us!

489
00:37:22.880 --> 00:37:24.330
He's right.

490
00:37:24.330 --> 00:37:26.260
We're friends!

491
00:37:26.260 --> 00:37:29.590
You're absolutely right. I'm sorry!

492
00:37:29.930 --> 00:37:34.350
It's just that you're not going to believe
what I'm about to say.

493
00:37:35.470 --> 00:37:37.230
What is it? Just say it!

494
00:37:41.940 --> 00:37:45.960
You know Kanjuro and Raizo.

495
00:37:45.960 --> 00:37:48.820
And the three of us here.

496
00:37:48.820 --> 00:37:50.660
The five of us...

497
00:37:51.360 --> 00:37:53.160
are really...

498
00:37:54.760 --> 00:37:57.120
from the past!

499
00:37:57.890 --> 00:37:58.460
Huh?

500
00:37:58.460 --> 00:37:59.680
– What?
– What?

501
00:37:59.680 --> 00:38:01.340
The past...?

502
00:38:01.340 --> 00:38:03.420
What do you mean by that?

503
00:38:10.640 --> 00:38:13.970
Retainer Kanjuro
Retainer Raizo
Kozuki Oden
Retainer Kin'emon
Kozuki Momonosuke
Grave of...

504
00:38:13.970 --> 00:38:15.270
Kin'emon

505
00:38:15.270 --> 00:38:16.520
Kanjuro

506
00:38:16.520 --> 00:38:17.810
Raizo

507
00:38:17.810 --> 00:38:19.190
Momonosuke

508
00:38:25.600 --> 00:38:30.450
The thing is, we are from a Wano
twenty years in the past...

509
00:38:31.580 --> 00:38:35.620
verily crossing through time
to the present day.

510
00:38:39.050 --> 00:38:39.790
Huh?!

511
00:38:41.250 --> 00:38:44.230
Huuuuuuh?!
